{"content": "<p>Foundation Friday helps get eyes on 👀 digital art on the <a href=\"https://foundation.app\">Foundation marketplace</a>. Let's get as many bids live 🧨 on Friday, so that by the end of the weekend, artists have sold a Foundation artwork. </p><p>Foundation Friday is about supporting artists by...</p><p><strong>🧨 1. </strong>Hit The Artist Follow Button on Foundation.<br /><strong>🧨 2. </strong>Tweet your art with #FoundationFriday or RT an artist post.<br /><strong>🧨 3. </strong>Make a bid if the art <em>moves</em> you. </p><p><strong>💥 Bonus Rule: </strong>Play 'bid roulette' and share your bid on Twitter if you dare.</p><p><a href=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/foundation-friday-3-rules/\">More background in this Foundation Friday article.</a></p><p>Here is a sample of some of the art available this Foundation Friday. Find more on the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23foundationfriday&amp;src=typed_query\">Twitter hashtag #FoundationFriday</a>. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2021/10/FA_QE3YVEAEVJyy.jpeg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"853\" height=\"1280\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2021/10/FA_QE3YVEAEVJyy.jpeg 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2021/10/FA_QE3YVEAEVJyy.jpeg 853w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://foundation.app/@_anand_krishnan/~/55413\">Anand Krishnan</a> - The lantern of the dawn</figcaption></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2021/10/FA-VuM2UYAYyaQL.jpeg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1638\" height=\"2048\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2021/10/FA-VuM2UYAYyaQL.jpeg 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2021/10/FA-VuM2UYAYy