on.app/@abhishekcjayaprakash/~/93395\">Dream by Abhishek C Jayaprakash&nbsp;</a></figcaption></figure><hr /><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/image\ns/2021/10/FA9JrAPUYAAw2_K.jpeg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"2500\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2021/10/FA9JrAPUYAAw2_K.jpeg 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2021/10/FA9JrAPUYAAw2_K.jpeg 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1600/2021/10/FA9JrAPUYAAw2_K.jpeg 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w2400/2021/10/FA9JrAPUYAAw2_K.jpeg 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://foundation.app/@tylersjourney/~/92108\">Ember - Tyler's Journey</a></figcaption></figure><p></p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-06-at-5.29.21-PM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1722\" height=\"1188\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-06-at-5.29.21-PM.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-06-at-5.29.21-PM.png 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1600/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-06-at-5.29.21-PM.png 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-06-at-5.29.21-PM.png 1722w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://foundation.app/@ApolloDubs\">Upside Down // Mirrors and Blindspotting // Mirrors by Jason Wong</a></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2021/10/nft-23.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1680\" height=\"1105\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2021/10/nft-23.jpg 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2021/10/nft-23.jpg 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1600/2021/10/nft-23.jpg 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2021/10/nft-23.jpg 1680w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://foundation.app/@RossFarnham/~/94401\">Skater Park by Ross Farnham</a></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2021/10/nft-21.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1680\" height=\"945\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2021/10/nft-21.jpg 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2021/10/nft-21.jpg 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1600/2021/10/nft-21.jpg 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2021/10/nft-21.jpg 1680w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://foundation.app/@ThinSlicePhoto/~/89949\">Baptism of Light by ThinSlicePhoto</a></figcaption></figure><p></p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2021/10/nft-22.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1680\" height=\"1680\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2021/10/nft-22.jpg 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2021/10/nft-22.jpg 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1600/2021/10/nft-22.jpg 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2021/10/nft-22.jpg 1680w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://foundation.app/@hosseinizaadi/~/63627\">Contradiction Vol. 2 by Hossein Izaadi</a></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-06-at-5.36.17-PM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1964\" height=\"1958\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-06-at-5.36.17-PM.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-06-at-5.36.17-PM.png 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1600/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-06-at-5.36.17-PM.png 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-06-at-5.36.17-PM.png 1964w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://foundation.app/@dailycreatics/~/92350\">&nbsp;Daily Leo by Daily Creatics</a></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2021/10/nft-24.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1680\" height=\"945\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2021/10/nft-24.jpg 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2021/10/nft-24.jpg 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1600/2021/10/nft-24.jpg 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2021/10/nft-24.jpg 1680w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://foundation.app/@artund/~/77988\">Sunday Morning by Artund</a></figcaption></figure><hr /><p><a href=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/#/portal/signup\">Subscribe to receive Mintface features free</a> by email.</p><p>If this article has made you curious about getting started with digital art, we also run the <a href=\"https://maven.com/cache/nft-digital-artist-economy\">Digital Artist Economy workshop</a> helping artists create their first digital art through a <a href=\"https://maven.com/cache/nft-digital-artist-economy\">three week programme.</a> Share it with an artist you'd like to see on an NFT marketplace.</p><p><strong>MintFace surfaces great artists and artworks so you don't have to. </strong></p><p><em>Enjoying MintFace? Help keep it free by supporting the platform in one of two ways.</em></p><p><strong>Art Collectors</strong> - you can become a member to receive a secret weekly MintFace  surfacing artwork that others have missed. No apes. No punks. Just quality art by quality artists.</p><p><strong>Artists</strong> - you can send any notes of appreciation to <strong><em>mintface.eth</em></strong> in whatever form you feel reflects your art.</p>"}